<h2 id="自增、自减"><a href="#自增、自减" class="headerlink" title="自增、自减"></a>自增、自减</h2><p>符号在前就先加/减，符号在后就后加/减</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">public static void main(String[] args) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        //符号在前就先加/减，符号在后就后加/减</span><br><span class="line">        //赋值</span><br><span class="line">        int a = 1;</span><br><span class="line">        int b = 10;</span><br><span class="line">        ++a;//自增 运算 ++a =a+1  a++ =a+1</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);//2</span><br><span class="line">        a++;//自增 运算</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);//3</span><br><span class="line">        b = ++a;//自增  赋值 b = (a+1);</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(b);//4</span><br><span class="line">        b = a++;//自增  赋值 b = a; a= a+1;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(b);//4</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a);//5</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





<h2 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h2><p>局部变量–》方法、方法参数</p>
<p>成员变量–》类中</p>
<h2 id="方法（函数）"><a href="#方法（函数）" class="headerlink" title="方法（函数）"></a>方法（函数）</h2><h2 id="类"><a href="#类" class="headerlink" title="类"></a>类</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/lingzhexi/blogImage/raw/master/2021/09/18/202109181042140.png" alt="img"></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Person</span></span>&#123; 	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">add</span><span class="params">()</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> a = <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">// 3</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> b = <span class="number">1</span>;   <span class="comment">// 4</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println( a+b );  <span class="comment">//1</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 调用方法 a = 3 b =4 进行加法运算</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addArg</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a, <span class="keyword">int</span> b)</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">    </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(a + b);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//主方法 程序执行的入口</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        addArg(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
